      "description": "ValidationResult comparing CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) against FDA generic centrifugal pump experimental measurements across 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean NIH prediction error was 8.3% with Monte Carlo 95th-percentile uncertainty band of ±14.1%. The validation was executed under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which is considered by the modelling team to be effectively the same build as the released version ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7; only a documentation patch and a non-physics solver flag were changed between the release candidate and the final release. No re-execution of the validation suite under the released build was performed prior to submission.",
